                        We specialize in crafting custom-tailored decor concepts across a wide range of events:
                    </p>

                    <ul class="service-list">
                        <li>
                            Grand Weddings & Mandaps: Elegant, majestic, and culturally rich setups designed to be the perfect backdrop for your sacred vows.
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            Birthday Celebrations & Theme Parties with unique decorations.
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            Corporate Events and Conference Decorations.
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            Engagement, Reception and Anniversary Decor.
                        </li>
                    </ul>

                    <p>
                        We have a dynamic marketing team and technical experts with years of experience and dedication.
                    </p>
                </div>

            </div>
            <!-- Image Section -->
            <div class="col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4">
