                         class="img-fluid"
                         alt="About Us">
                </div>
            </div>
        </div> 

        <div class="row align-items-center m-4">

            <!-- Image Section -->
            <div class="col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-4">
                <div class="about-image">
                    <img src="https://shopnetindia.com/design_img/inner-abt-01.jpg"
                         class="img-fluid"
                         alt="About Us">
                </div>
            </div>
            <!-- Content Section -->
            <div class="col-12 col-md-12 col-lg-8 mb-4 mb-lg-0">
                <div class="about-content">
                    <h2>Why Choose Khushi Decoration?</h2>
                    <p>
                        Tailored Concepts: No two love stories are the same, and neither should your decor be. We work hand-in-hand with you to bring your specific vision to life.
                    </p>
                    <ul class="service-list">
                        <li>
                            Premium Quality Materials: We source the freshest, most vibrant natural flowers, high-quality drapes, and cutting-edge lighting equipment to ensure everything looks flawless.
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            Flawless Execution: Our highly trained and passionate decorators handle everything from transport to setup and teardown, letting you relax and fully enjoy your big day.
                        </li>

                        <li>
                            Affordable Luxury: We believe that stunning decor shouldn’t have to cost a fortune. We offer versatile packages designed to fit a variety of budgets without compromising on elegance.
                        </li>
                    </ul>
                    <p>
                        We have a dynamic marketing team and technical experts with years of experience and dedication.
                    </p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>
